<div class="grid-wrapper">
  	<main role="main" class="grid grid-2-3">
		<header>
			<h1 class="heading-xlarge">Search for an apprenticeship</h1>
		</header>
		<article>
			<p>Find out how much funding you're entitled to by searching for your apprentice below.</p>

            <section>
                <details>
                    <summary>How to choose a standard</summary>
                    <div class="panel-indent" id="helpText" role="region" aria-hidden="false">
                        <p>Standards show what apprentices will learn during their apprenticeships.</p>

                        <section>
                            <h3 class="heading-medium">How standards are delivered</h3>

                            <p>Training providers teach the skills listed in standards.</p>

                            <p>You donâ€™t have to choose a local provider. Many of them offer distance learning.</p>

                            <p>Sometimes providers will come to you to train your apprentice. At other times your apprentice will travel to them.</p>

                            <p><a href="#Standard">Find a training provider</a></p>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h3 class="heading-medium">What can you deliver yourself?</h3>

                            <p>You can carry out training yourself, but it could affect your funding.</p>

                            <p>You can also assess your apprentice in-house, but you must:</p>
                            <ul class="list-bullet">
                                <li>do it impartially</li>
                                <li>involve a third party</li>
                                <li>provide supporting evidence like employee records</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </details>
            </section>

			<form id="standardSearchForm" method="GET" action="/employer/search-mid-results.html">
				<fieldset class="">
					<div class="form-group section-border">
    					<label class="heading-small" for="Keywords">Which job role would your apprentice have?</label>
    					<span class="form-hint" id="StandardHint">eg. <em>"carpenter"</em> or <em>"engineer"</em>.</span>
						<input autofocus="autofocus" class="form-control" data-val="true" data-val-regex="'Keywords' contains some invalid characters" data-val-regex-pattern="^[\w\s]+$" id="Standard" name="Standard" type="text" value="">
                        <p><a href="#">Browse by industry / sector</a></p>
					</div>

				</fieldset>
                <section class="get-started">
                        <button type="submit" class="button">Search for an apprenticeship</button>
                </section>
			</form>
		</article>
  	</main>
  	<div class="related-container grid grid-1-3">
		<div class="related">
	  		{{> info-links}}
  		</div>
  	</div>
